# The sandbox image's build context is this directory. Send the Dockerfile and
# the shim *source* (including the vendored sandbox-protocol.ts copy), but
# nothing else — no host files, no secrets, and never the shim's local build
# artifacts or installed deps (they are reinstalled/rebuilt in-image for the
# correct platform).
*
!Dockerfile
!shim/
shim/node_modules/
shim/dist/
